org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord
Interface IAeRegistrationResponse

All Known Implementing Classes:
AeRegistrationResponse
public interface IAeRegistrationResponse

Interface for a WS-Coordination registation response. Note: This is an internal implementation tailored to be used with requirement 111 i.e. the interface provides a simple property getter and setter. The final implementation should follow something close to the RegisterResponse definition as per http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2004/10/wsoor. Maybe refactor this interface to wsio.IWebServiceCoordRegistrationResponse.
